						               													<description>Dragon Ball Z - Smash Battle is a tabletop game of super detailed miniature superheroes and villains battling against each other.  Players fight with each other with special event cards, fighting skills, defending skill in an exciting contest of strategy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is a game designed for 2 to 4 players.  Each player takes control of his own faction of miniatures fighting in the famous Dragon Ball Z scene - Battle Arena.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GAME PLAY:&amp;#10;Build up your own team and game set up&amp;#10;&amp;#10;4 Phases per Round:&amp;#10;PHASE 1. Event Phase - Dragon Ball Story Scenario&amp;#10;Draw an Event Card from the deck.  Each Event Card does not only tell a scenario of the DBZ story, but it also affects the characters in that round.  It might be a mission of collecting Dragon Ball, Saiyan turns to Great Ape, Ginyu Force Team sudden attack and more.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;PHASE 2. Initial Phase - Prepare for Battle:&amp;#10;Set up the action sequence of characters.  The action sequence is critical and players have to apply their strategy in the next action phase&amp;#10;&amp;#10;PHASE 3. Action Phase - Moving and Battling:&amp;#10;Each character comes with a character card which lists all of attributes, fighting skills and abilities.  Players apply their strategy along with the characteristics of each character in the combat of each battle.&amp;#10;Not only can players calculate the result of the battle by referencing the characters' card data with the rule book, but players can also apply the Augmented Reality (AR) app to get the battle result easily.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;PHASE 4. Refresh Phase - Finalize the battling result and refresh for next round:&amp;#10;Finalize all the damages and results from the previous phase, and refresh the energy if needed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
